Title: U.S. set to hand over Internet’s naming system to ICANN
Content: The U.S. is set to cede power of the Internet’s naming system to a non-profit organisation on October 1, ending the almost 20-year process to hand over a crucial part of the Internet’s governance.
Author: PTI
